WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 40=

02:09.900 --> 02:10.990
I know you've been afraid

02:10.990 --> 02:11.830
that I'd forget you.

02:14.110 --> 02:15.460
You aren't willing to be

02:15.460 --> 02:16.670
the 23rd partner I've lost.

02:18.390 --> 02:19.740
You want to be my only love.

02:20.580 --> 02:21.830
You want me to remember you.

02:23.040 --> 02:23.900
But you don't want me

02:23.900 --> 02:25.420
to be stuck in the memory of parting.

02:26.960 --> 02:27.830
Is that why

02:27.830 --> 02:28.700
you kept silent?

02:33.460 --> 02:34.830
I was afraid that you'd forget me.

02:40.790 --> 02:41.950
But now, I'm afraid

02:47.270 --> 02:48.510
that you'll always remember.

02:50.230 --> 02:51.230
I can't forget you.

02:54.830 --> 02:56.140
I remember everything about you.

02:58.790 --> 02:59.900
Fireworks and lanterns.

03:01.860 --> 03:03.140
Scent of flowers and wine.

03:04.950 --> 03:06.180
Blood and wedding gown.

03:08.070 --> 03:09.140
Ball and sunlight.

03:11.740 --> 03:13.020
I remember your breath,

03:14.950 --> 03:15.790
your heartbeat,

03:16.830 --> 03:17.670
your pulse,

03:18.390 --> 03:19.230
your warmth,

03:19.990 --> 03:20.830
your scent,

03:22.950 --> 03:23.790
your smile,

03:24.580 --> 03:25.860
your wild talk and whispers,

03:27.020 --> 03:28.510
your pleas and coquetry.

03:31.300 --> 03:32.270
I don't want to forget.

03:34.430 --> 03:35.270
I don't want it all

03:35.270 --> 03:36.460
to fade into dust.

04:05.700 --> 04:06.540
Foxy.

04:09.070 --> 04:09.910
Let's get married,

04:10.790 --> 04:11.630
shall we?

04:22.380 --> 04:23.220
Yes.

04:46.710 --> 04:49.420
It is time!

05:25.500 --> 05:29.020
(Sovereign's Hall)

06:11.950 --> 06:17.810
ظآزTouched memories linger like shadowsظآز

06:18.440 --> 06:23.950
ظآزScattered reflections
sink into my heartظآز

06:24.540 --> 06:26.540
ظآزIf I couldظآز

06:26.540 --> 06:30.550
ظآزSoftly call you like thisظآز

06:31.640 --> 06:36.250
ظآزAs gentle as a fleeting embraceظآز

06:37.110 --> 06:39.870
ظآزEven if the day gives way to nightظآز

06:39.870 --> 06:41.520
ظآزGrows dim and fades awayظآز

06:41.520 --> 06:44.350
ظآزWhat would come of it?ظآز

06:44.760 --> 06:46.260
ظآزI care for no one but youظآز

06:46.260 --> 06:47.910
ظآزI'll come near and run to youظآز

06:47.910 --> 06:51.090
ظآزTo heal the deepest woundsظآز

06:51.610 --> 06:54.300
ظآزMiracles, eternity, and radianceظآز

06:54.300 --> 06:57.050
ظآزWorth more than any barren landظآز

06:57.290 --> 06:59.650
ظآزI might as well
spend the rest of my lifeظآز

06:59.650 --> 07:03.620
ظآزWalking with you through eternityظآز

08:43.540 --> 08:44.710
(The one I love is)

08:45.620 --> 08:46.500
(natural sound,)

08:47.230 --> 08:48.070
(frozen water,)

08:49.020 --> 08:49.860
(blazing heat,)

08:51.110 --> 08:52.020
(fragrant wine...)

08:52.020 --> 08:53.140
(Sovereign's Hall)

08:53.140 --> 08:54.110
(And precious food.)

08:55.590 --> 08:56.660
(Black and white,)

08:57.540 --> 08:58.710
(red and yellow,)

09:00.190 --> 09:02.500
(he's the harmony of all colors.)

09:05.070 --> 09:06.350
(When I first fell for her,)

09:07.780 --> 09:09.350
(she was holding a little pinwheel)

09:10.830 --> 09:11.950
(and twirling toward me)

09:12.540 --> 09:13.830
(in the blazing sun.)

09:15.380 --> 09:16.500
(In that very moment,)

09:17.590 --> 09:18.540
(I felt this world)

09:18.540 --> 09:19.380
(was wonderful.)

09:20.710 --> 09:21.740
(And she was the reason)

09:23.020 --> 09:24.190
(that made it happen.)

09:26.020 --> 09:27.740
(She's a really, really wonderful girl.)

09:29.950 --> 09:31.350
(She's the only thing)

09:32.990 --> 09:34.430
(I've wished to have.)

10:09.140 --> 10:10.500
Bound by fate,

10:10.860 --> 10:12.230
this is a perfect match!

10:24.990 --> 10:26.780
Bride and groom, bow to each other!

10:30.410 --> 10:34.190
ظآزSpring comes; ice and snow thawظآز

10:35.920 --> 10:41.750
ظآزAll things wake, with the east windظآز

10:44.960 --> 10:48.960
ظآزIn the season at its fullestظآز

10:49.070 --> 10:50.260
The ceremony is done!

10:50.490 --> 10:56.880
ظآزLight the lamps to pierce the old nightظآز

11:01.370 --> 11:08.440
ظآزBorrow mortal warmth to ease the coldظآز

11:08.680 --> 11:15.750
ظآزWarm winds bring fragrant bloomsظآز

11:15.940 --> 11:23.060
ظآزLet me love with all my heart
in youthful graceظآز

11:23.860 --> 11:24.950
I'm yours now,

11:28.430 --> 11:29.270
Your Grace.

11:31.560 --> 11:34.580
ظآزWith you by my sideظآز

11:47.660 --> 11:48.500
Duan Shunxi,

11:50.230 --> 11:52.020
I'll spend my whole life loving you

11:53.950 --> 11:54.950
and never forget you.

11:55.970 --> 11:59.470
ظآزIn your eyesظآز

12:03.200 --> 12:07.750
ظآزIf you'd let me know how to tellظآز

12:08.560 --> 12:16.590
ظآزThe difference between spring
and autumn, love and worryظآز

12:17.580 --> 12:24.760
ظآزBorrow mortal warmth to ease the coldظآز

12:25.010 --> 12:27.830
ظآزWarm winds bring fragrant bloomsظآز

12:27.860 --> 12:28.700
How wonderful.

12:28.710 --> 12:29.580
Yeah.

12:34.590 --> 12:39.710
ظآزA pot of wine in fleeting dreamsظآز

12:41.280 --> 12:49.700
ظآزA brief life dares seek eternityظآز

12:50.370 --> 12:57.410
ظآزBorrow one lovely dream,
let me savor this fleeting joyظآز

12:57.770 --> 13:04.700
ظآزMay I roam drunk in dreams and
never forgetظآز

13:04.980 --> 13:12.100
ظآزPlease ferry me once through this lifeظآز

13:12.290 --> 13:22.080
ظآزIn the netherworld, I see a rayظآز

13:24.370 --> 13:27.100
ظآزTo what home shall I returnظآز

13:33.230 --> 13:34.070
It's like a dream.

13:48.230 --> 13:49.070
Are you insane?

13:49.590 --> 13:50.900
You gave me all five senses.

13:51.190 --> 13:52.260
Considering your health,

13:52.260 --> 13:53.190
you won't survive a day.

13:53.190 --> 13:54.030
I know.

13:55.860 --> 13:57.380
Fengyi must have a death wish.

13:57.860 --> 13:58.700
Don't blame him.

13:59.540 --> 14:00.500
I forced him.

14:09.190 --> 14:10.030
Simu,

14:11.900 --> 14:13.620
I know you write your journal

14:14.780 --> 14:16.020
every night after I fall asleep.

14:17.170 --> 14:18.020
The one you suspended

14:18.020 --> 14:19.110
300 years ago.

14:20.430 --> 14:21.710
You record daily little things

14:24.430 --> 14:25.620
like you did before.

14:28.950 --> 14:29.950
You put down every detail

14:29.950 --> 14:30.790
we've shared.

14:35.470 --> 14:36.310
That's wonderful.

14:47.740 --> 14:48.990
I want this journal

14:51.070 --> 14:52.310
to record more sweet memories.

14:55.260 --> 14:56.190
To me, this world

14:57.780 --> 14:58.740
is a present.

15:03.540 --> 15:05.070
I want to give it to you.

15:09.660 --> 15:10.780
With all five senses,

15:12.710 --> 15:13.780
you can completely feel

15:13.780 --> 15:14.620
what it's like to live.

15:23.620 --> 15:24.500
You just can't

15:24.500 --> 15:25.540
have a moment's rest.

15:29.500 --> 15:30.340
Otherwise,

15:31.800 --> 15:32.660
how could I

15:32.660 --> 15:33.860
stir up these lifeless days

15:35.310 --> 15:36.380
in the Void?

15:48.660 --> 15:49.860
It's so cold here.

15:52.260 --> 15:53.310
I already miss the warmth

15:53.310 --> 15:54.260
of the Mortal World.

15:59.190 --> 16:00.030
All right.

16:02.540 --> 16:03.380
Let's go there then.

16:25.780 --> 16:26.620
Lady Jiang Ai,

16:28.230 --> 16:29.110
it's a perfect moment.

16:29.830 --> 16:31.090
Get us more good wine.

16:31.860 --> 16:32.950
Still want some wine

16:32.950 --> 16:33.920
when you're this frail?

16:37.350 --> 16:39.590
Give us the Cloud Wine you've treasured.

17:45.910 --> 17:46.950
Golden sun.

17:58.710 --> 18:00.100
The sunlight is so warm.

18:10.950 --> 18:11.820
What's that sound?

18:18.910 --> 18:20.260
Woodcutters have come up here.

18:22.740 --> 18:24.100
They're singing folk songs.

18:33.540 --> 18:34.430
What's that smell?

18:37.820 --> 18:39.390
It's the smell of mortal life.

19:04.580 --> 19:05.420
Would you like some?

19:10.100 --> 19:11.500
In this world, the bride and groom

19:12.340 --> 19:13.390
cross their cups.

19:42.630 --> 19:44.340
This kind of life will still be blissful

19:45.190 --> 19:46.390
even in a century, won't it?

20:00.580 --> 20:01.420
Simu.

20:05.230 --> 20:06.470
What do you think of this world?

20:11.340 --> 20:12.180
It's wonderful.

20:14.060 --> 20:14.900
Just like a home.

20:17.580 --> 20:18.470
Your life

20:20.020 --> 20:21.540
was full of misfortunes.

20:24.300 --> 20:25.390
And you sacrificed your life

20:26.780 --> 20:28.580
to give me brightness and vitality.

20:30.470 --> 20:32.390
Do you think all these misfortunes

20:36.910 --> 20:38.060
finally led to me?

20:45.060 --> 20:46.670
Do you regret meeting me?

20:58.230 --> 20:59.870
You're the only luck I've had

21:03.780 --> 21:04.710
in my difficult life.

21:09.990 --> 21:11.260
If life started over and over,

21:12.540 --> 21:13.820
I would still wish to meet you.

21:20.020 --> 21:20.860
Every time.

21:23.260 --> 21:24.100
A thousand times.

21:26.670 --> 21:27.510
What about you?

21:30.470 --> 21:31.710
If life could start over,

21:34.740 --> 21:35.910
would you still meet me?

21:36.670 --> 21:37.510
Yes.

21:38.500 --> 21:39.780
No matter how many times,

21:41.630 --> 21:42.670
I would hold your hand

21:42.670 --> 21:43.540
and pull you up

21:44.540 --> 21:45.990
on that New Year's Eve.

21:47.820 --> 21:49.260
I'd also hold you right now

21:50.540 --> 21:51.780
and be with you for a lifetime.

21:53.430 --> 21:54.340
I would be sad.

21:56.390 --> 21:57.540
But I would never regret it.

22:31.310 --> 22:35.020
ظآزFalling down like snowظآز

22:35.490 --> 22:38.970
ظآزJoys and sorrows of the mortal worldظآز

22:38.970 --> 22:42.850
ظآزSwept along by the daylightظآز

22:45.020 --> 22:45.870
Duan Shunxi.

22:48.260 --> 22:49.260
Don't leave.

22:51.470 --> 22:53.060
Stay with me.

22:54.060 --> 22:55.060
Duan Shunxi!

22:55.390 --> 22:56.230
Thank you.

22:57.260 --> 22:58.100
Does it still hurt?

22:58.710 --> 22:59.550
No.

22:59.950 --> 23:01.150
Can't you let me win once?

23:01.950 --> 23:03.060
All right.

23:05.260 --> 23:06.100
Duan Shunxi,

23:06.910 --> 23:08.100
I love being with you.

23:09.560 --> 23:13.180
ظآزLonging to meet, yet parted by destinyظآز

23:13.690 --> 23:17.300
ظآزLet me wander throughظآز

23:17.300 --> 23:20.940
ظآزLight and dark,┬بwithout turning backظآز

23:21.350 --> 23:24.750
ظآزWander to the other shore
with the lanternظآز

23:24.880 --> 23:27.660
ظآزAccompanied by eternityظآز

23:27.670 --> 23:28.510
So...

23:29.090 --> 23:31.780
ظآزAs all things turn and flowظآز

23:34.870 --> 23:36.740
We've lived out this life.

23:40.230 --> 23:41.070
So...

23:43.430 --> 23:44.870
I stayed with you until I grew old.

23:50.990 --> 23:51.830
Simu.

23:52.000 --> 23:55.000
ظآزDawn and dusk rise and setظآز

23:55.020 --> 23:55.860
Thank you.

23:55.860 --> 23:59.280
ظآزLonging to meet, yet parted by destinyظآز

23:59.910 --> 24:01.910
Thank you for coming back to me.

24:03.360 --> 24:06.840
ظآزLight and dark,┬بwithout turning backظآز

24:06.870 --> 24:07.780
Duan Shunxi.

24:09.670 --> 24:10.630
You...

24:10.910 --> 24:12.470
Don't leave me, all right?

24:13.300 --> 24:14.500
Don't leave me.

24:15.190 --> 24:16.670
Stay with me, will you?

24:17.930 --> 24:21.510
ظآزWhether I stay or go, I'm all aloneظآز

24:21.540 --> 24:23.390
It's all right.

24:24.740 --> 24:25.580
It's just all right.

24:25.780 --> 24:26.780
You'll be all right.

24:29.020 --> 24:30.230
You'll be fine.

24:37.150 --> 24:37.990
Simu.

24:40.870 --> 24:41.710
Thank you.

24:44.580 --> 24:45.670
With you by my side,

24:45.670 --> 24:46.950
I've never lost a bet.

24:50.630 --> 24:51.470
Promise me.

24:53.300 --> 24:55.150
You'll remember the world as it is now.

24:59.780 --> 25:00.780
After I'm gone...

25:01.000 --> 25:03.680
ظآزSwept along by the daylightظآز

25:03.710 --> 25:05.760
This will always be your home.

25:05.760 --> 25:09.120
ظآزThe forms and hues of the mortal realmظآز

25:09.300 --> 25:12.190
ظآزLingering for a fleeting momentظآز

25:12.190 --> 25:16.000
ظآزWas once touched by laughing tearsظآز

25:16.020 --> 25:16.860
Please don't.

25:16.860 --> 25:19.950
ظآزIf I could live a simple lifeظآز

25:19.950 --> 25:20.800
ظآزFor onceظآز

25:20.800 --> 25:25.650
ظآزI'd be a guest in a sweet dreamظآز

25:25.950 --> 25:29.560
ظآزDawn and dusk rise and setظآز

25:29.730 --> 25:33.610
ظآزLonging to meet, yet parted by destinyظآز

25:33.840 --> 25:37.410
ظآزLet me wander throughظآز

25:37.410 --> 25:40.460
ظآزLight and dark,┬بwithout turning backظآز

25:40.670 --> 25:41.510
Duan Shunxi.

25:41.510 --> 25:43.750
ظآزWander to the other shore
with the lanternظآز

25:43.820 --> 25:44.660
Duan Shunxi.

25:45.910 --> 25:46.750
Duan Shunxi.

25:47.710 --> 25:48.670
I'm here.

25:48.670 --> 25:50.190
Don't leave me!

25:53.340 --> 25:54.300
Stay with me!

25:54.670 --> 25:56.180
No. You can't leave me.

25:56.820 --> 25:57.950
I won't let you leave me.

26:00.740 --> 26:01.580
No!

26:02.230 --> 26:03.070
No!

26:07.300 --> 26:08.500
Take my hand.

26:09.060 --> 26:10.580
Don't leave me!

26:11.190 --> 26:13.710
Stay with me!

26:14.580 --> 26:17.190
Who can help him?

26:20.150 --> 26:21.390
No!

26:22.430 --> 26:23.540
Duan Shunxi,

26:23.910 --> 26:25.910
open your eyes and look at me.

26:26.430 --> 26:28.340
Don't leave me.

26:30.390 --> 26:31.950
Duan Shunxi,

26:32.870 --> 26:35.060
open your eyes.

26:35.280 --> 26:37.660
ظآزMoments may lastظآز

26:37.740 --> 26:39.150
I won't let you leave.

26:40.060 --> 26:41.990
I just won't.

26:43.060 --> 26:44.060
Duan Shunxi.

26:45.150 --> 26:47.710
Don't take his life!

26:52.990 --> 26:55.300
Give him back to me!

26:56.300 --> 26:57.950
No!

29:17.580 --> 29:19.340
(Is this how you feel now?)

29:20.670 --> 29:22.390
(I burned brightly throughout my life)

29:23.710 --> 29:25.230
(and thought I'd have no regrets.)

29:27.470 --> 29:28.430
(But in this moment...)

29:30.780 --> 29:31.620
(Simu,)

29:33.710 --> 29:34.710
(I'm regretting it.)

29:37.470 --> 29:38.910
(I can't let you hurt like this.)

29:41.820 --> 29:43.300
(I'll find my way back to you.)

32:32.670 --> 32:34.670
Greetings, Your Grace.

32:38.870 --> 32:39.710
From this day on,

32:41.150 --> 32:42.630
I'll no longer command the Void.

32:44.150 --> 32:45.020
What?

32:45.020 --> 32:45.950
But...

32:45.950 --> 32:46.820
But why?

32:47.470 --> 32:48.950
The new sovereign has appeared.

33:04.540 --> 33:05.540
Chenying has absorbed

33:05.540 --> 33:06.500
the Lantern's power.

33:07.150 --> 33:07.990
From this day on,

33:08.950 --> 33:10.580
he'll be the new sovereign.

33:16.060 --> 33:17.340
The Lantern has chosen him.

33:17.780 --> 33:18.990
But he isn't senior enough.

33:18.990 --> 33:19.870
Yeah. That's right.

33:38.350 --> 33:43.200
ظآزSpirits are intoxicatedظآز

33:43.370 --> 33:47.020
ظآزWith obsessionsظآز

33:49.800 --> 33:54.750
ظآزForget the form to achieveظآز

33:54.970 --> 33:58.920
ظآزYet I can'tظآز

34:00.390 --> 34:02.540
Hail to the new sovereign!
Greetings, Your Lordship!

34:04.950 --> 34:07.820
Hail to the new sovereign!
Greetings, Your Lordship!

34:08.390 --> 34:11.580
Hail to the new sovereign!
Greetings, Your Lordship!

34:12.060 --> 34:15.140
Hail to the new sovereign!
Greetings, Your Lordship!

34:15.620 --> 34:18.620
Hail to the new sovereign!
Greetings, Your Lordship!

34:19.390 --> 34:22.790
Hail to the new sovereign!
Greetings, Your Lordship!

34:54.620 --> 34:55.460
I think

34:55.620 --> 34:56.540
that spirit aura

34:56.540 --> 34:57.950
feels like Xu's.

34:58.790 --> 34:59.630
What do you think,

34:59.990 --> 35:00.830
Lady Jiang Ai?

35:02.020 --> 35:03.500
He is dead.

35:03.950 --> 35:05.350
Even if he had deep obsessions,

35:05.910 --> 35:08.430
he wouldn't appear
before Simu, theoretically.

35:09.700 --> 35:10.540
Yeah.

35:12.100 --> 35:12.940
Lady Jiang Ai,

35:13.470 --> 35:14.310
you're right.

35:15.700 --> 35:16.620
But I believe

35:18.060 --> 35:19.020
even if Xu is dead,

35:20.430 --> 35:21.500
he will come back.

35:22.620 --> 35:23.660
He'll stay with Simu.

35:26.430 --> 35:27.270
That makes sense.

35:27.950 --> 35:29.060
He's been like this

35:29.870 --> 35:31.140
his whole life.

35:31.870 --> 35:32.870
Unpredictable.

35:40.690 --> 35:41.540
How beautiful.

35:41.540 --> 35:42.700
Is this easy to raise?

35:42.790 --> 35:43.660
Yes.

35:43.660 --> 35:44.540
It only needs water.

35:45.430 --> 35:46.270
That's good.

35:46.870 --> 35:47.870
So many kinds.

35:48.950 --> 35:49.990
- Take your pick.
- Sure.

35:49.990 --> 35:51.700
Fragrant sachets and pendants.

35:51.700 --> 35:52.660
Fruit.

35:52.660 --> 35:53.660
Miss, take a look.

35:53.660 --> 35:55.900
Come take a look. Fresh fruit.

35:55.900 --> 35:57.180
(Prosperous)
Come take a look.

35:57.180 --> 35:58.180
Sweet, I promise.

35:58.430 --> 36:00.180
- I'll take that.
- Sure.

36:00.180 --> 36:01.350
Come on, Miss. Take a look.

36:02.500 --> 36:03.430
There's a new sovereign.

36:04.470 --> 36:05.310
Since then,

36:06.700 --> 36:08.100
she has only been He Simu.

36:09.620 --> 36:10.540
I deeply hope

36:10.910 --> 36:11.990
she will have happiness.

36:12.700 --> 36:13.750
Even if this happiness

36:14.180 --> 36:15.220
isn't perfect at all.

36:16.390 --> 36:17.540
Hope remains anyway.

36:25.870 --> 36:26.990
When fate permits,

36:28.580 --> 36:29.660
the one she lost may return.

36:31.910 --> 36:32.750
What do you think,

36:33.830 --> 36:34.670
Goddess?

36:45.140 --> 36:46.140
Through destiny,

36:46.990 --> 36:47.830
all things arise.

36:50.870 --> 36:51.710
Perhaps.

36:58.620 --> 37:02.340
ظآزFalling down like snowظآز

